<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2012/06/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>CleanArchitecture.JwtAuth.Template</id>
    <version>1.0.0</version>
    <title>Clean Architecture Web API with JWT Auth</title>
    <authors>Jabbar Huseynzada</authors>
    <description>A production-ready .NET 9 Web API template with Clean Architecture, JWT Authentication with Refresh Tokens, CQRS with MediatR, PostgreSQL, Unit of Work, Soft Delete, Audit Logging, Caching (Redis/InMemory), Rate Limiting, Background Jobs (Hangfire), Response Compression, OpenTelemetry, and Health Checks.</description>
    <releaseNotes>
v1.0.0:
- Clean Architecture with Domain, Application, Infrastructure, WebApi layers
- JWT Authentication with refresh token rotation
- CQRS pattern with MediatR
- FluentValidation for request validation
- Unit of Work pattern with transaction support
- Soft Delete with automatic query filtering
- Audit Logging (CreatedAt, CreatedBy, ModifiedAt, ModifiedBy, DeletedAt, DeletedBy)
- Pagination (PagedRequest/PagedResult)
- Caching with Redis or In-Memory support
- Rate Limiting (fixed, sliding, token bucket, per-IP)
- Background Jobs with Hangfire and PostgreSQL storage
- Response Compression (Brotli/Gzip)
- OpenTelemetry for distributed tracing and metrics
- Serilog structured logging (console and file)
- API versioning (URL, header, query string)
- Global exception handling middleware
- Health check endpoints (live, ready, detailed)
- PostgreSQL with Entity Framework Core
- Docker support with pgAdmin
- Password reset with email verification
    </releaseNotes>
